      "span_text": "Extent of host cell lysis was estimated indirectly by measuring the release of intracellular lactate dehydrogenase from the nucleated cells using Cytox® Membrane Permeability Assay from Promega, Madison, USA (Product No. G7890) as described elsewhere [CITATION_1] ."
